    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Surveyors' measuring devices consisting of 100 steel links each 7.92 inches long joined in a chain 66 feet long; precursors of engineers' chains.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
